    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Magical Animal Farm is timed survival game with some rouge-lite elements and long term progression. Magic has come back to the world, bringing forth all sorts of creatures to tear apart your once precious farmstead. Can you survive and make it whole? Survive each round and upgrade your farm and improve your armaments! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >RELEASE THE GOATS! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><u><strong>Features</strong></u> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Fast paced combat</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Quick rounds </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Multiple unique play-styles through diverse weapon selection </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Variety of items to collect every run</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Farm-themed long term progression </p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Colorful, 64-bit art style</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Endless replay-ability </p></li></ul>",
